Author: dukeleto#7326
Content: it's possible to overclock batch 3 z9 mini's via `ssh`, at least to 550. More requires binary patching the `cgminer` binary :abusedsmily:

Author: dukeleto#7326
Content:
```ssh to miner.
edit /config/cgminer.conf
see bitmain-freq in config file, change value.
save file.
"/etc/init.d/cgminer.sh restart"```
